---
import RecentOtome from "../components/RecentOtome.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "tunnel of love";
const subtitle = "otome";
const bannerImage = "/bg/wonderful_land_41.gif";
const tinyImage = "/smalls/sm-dripheart.gif";
---

<Layout
    title={title}
    subtitle={subtitle}
    bannerImage={bannerImage}
    tinyImage={tinyImage}
>
    <div slot="main-text">
        <div class="flexbox">
            <p>
                why classify otome in a different section of the park? well
                first of all i wanted to pay tribute to the iconography of the
                tunnel of love. i think they're just hilariously specific. like
                ... really what a concept. you know what this park needs? a
                private space to bone.
            </p>
            <div class="center"><img src="/images/swan.gif" /></div>

            <p>
                also i wanted the spicier content to exist separately from the
                other sfw things. it just felt weird putting up half naked sylus
                next to tom nook you know?
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div slot="full">
        <h2>memorable games</h2>
        <div class="flexbox" style="flex-direction: row;">
            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img src="/images/whatdyousaycaleb.png" />
                </div>
                <div class="center">
                    <h4>
                        <a href="/posts/post-o1/">love and deepspace</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://www.allkeyshop.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/diabolik-lovers-chaos-lineage-nintendo-switch-800x500-4.jpg"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>diabolik lovers*</h4></div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://capiora.ru/userfiles/local/a/Mystic-Messenger.jpg"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>mystic messenger</h4></div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/c_fill,w_1200/q_auto:best/f_auto/dpr_2.0/ncom/software/switch/70010000022647/8e47b9480fcbd50087c4aff74bf95e054e5c1a941e1dc2e1ecc019ad049c7ee3"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>code realize</h4></div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311350/ss_ad97f2f4d298a3bb443dd5898168eba146ecd056.1920x1080.jpg?t=1684463689"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center">
                    <h4>kissed by the<br /> baddest bidder</h4>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://64.media.tumblr.com/5925b99301a07a3be37cd51d6e3932da/tumblr_inline_p9iq2rlXB81t6rnmr_540.jpg"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>rose in the embers</h4></div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://s2.qwant.com/thumbr/474x266/4/b/f072a68780c3a8c6eddbdc9c30094328bdc6a71f1d796948cbc8f73d1089be/OIP.g3pJCEjgVRA-sYsArf_ZyAHaEK.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse.mm.bing.net%2Fth%2Fid%2FOIP.g3pJCEjgVRA-sYsArf_ZyAHaEK%3Fr%3D0%26pid%3DApi&q=0&b=1&p=0&a=0"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>obey me</h4></div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="shrine">
                    <img
                        src="https://www.pockettactics.com/wp-content/sites/pockettactics/2022/05/otome-games-nu-carnival-550x309.jpg"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="center"><h4>nu carnival</h4></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <br />
        *this game falls weirdly inbetween horror and otome due to extremely dark
        elements, sensitive viewers beware
    </div>

    <div slot="left-half">
        <h2>wishlist</h2>
        <p>otomes i either need to play or need to finish a single route</p>
        <ul>
            <li>ikemen sengoku</li>
            <li>collar x mallice</li>
            <li>love unholyc</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div slot="right-half">
        <div class="posts-grid">
            <RecentOtome />
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
